The fact that she is white has drawn criticism from some blacks who see the marriage as evidence that Clarence Thomas has rejected his roots. Some religious-rights groups are troubled by her anti-cult activities in light of her former involvement with Lifespring, a motivational group. They see a woman with strong opinions on issues that are bound to come before the court. ; Virginia Thomas has represented the conservative viewpoint in her jobs as a staffer for a Republican congressman, spokeswoman at the US Chamber of Congress and deputy assistant secretary at the Department of Labor. 